    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, road-worthy condition and is ready to serve as a dependable daily driver for its next owner. The engine starts reliably and runs well, though it would benefit from a standard tune-up in the near future. The interior shows some expected wear and tear, including minor stains and scuffs on the upholstery, and the exterior has a few noticeable scratches and small dings consistent with its age. All major systems are functional, though some minor features like the rear window defrost are currently non-operational. Overall, it's a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for reliable transportation without the high price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 21000.0,
